      "activities-page-description": "At Harvest Schools we believe that a great part of any learning journey is health and activeness. that is why we provide stunning facilities for all kinds of activities accompanied by trainers for all the learning stages, including kindergarten. However, Activities should not affect students' school performance during the week days, therefore, Harvest Academy operates mostly during weekend times. In addition of course to all P.E. lessons through out the week.Students are allowed to join any time of the year through the form below. Or by contacting: ",
